These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking, writing
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | writing | woodworking | gardening | skydiving | singing |

