.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

