.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the german##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the polish##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

