.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, disco, dubstep, indie
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bike, helicopter, ship, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person driving the taxi is the fan of disco##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | disco | blues      | classical  | indie | dubstep |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi  | snowmobile | helicopter | ship  | bike    |

