.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, hiking, singing, traveling, woodworking
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, electronic, house, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | traveling | filmmaking | hiking  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | electronic  | disco  | classical | house      | country |

