1. the mexican is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the american##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the australian is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the german is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

