.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, guinea-pig, horse, snake, turtle
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, roller, ship, snowmobile, trike
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person driving the trike##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Transport   | motorbike | snowmobile | trike | roller     | bike  | ship       |

