.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, funk, hip-hop, punk, reggae, salsa
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the fan of salsa##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | ambient  | reggae     | hip-hop    | funk  | punk          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

