.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, thriller, western, zombie
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person watching family movies##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | family | zombie | western | satire | thriller |

