The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, librarian, manager, pilot, writer
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
4. the librarian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the manager##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up     | juice | almond-milk | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Job        | writer | manager | pilot | librarian   | coach    | fisherman |

