.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-16::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles, reading, rock-climbing
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, parkour, skateboarding, skiing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Hobby   | reading | magic-tricks | fishing  | rock-climbing | puzzles       | hiking   |
| Sport   | parkour | lacrosse     | handball | skiing        | skateboarding | swimming |

