5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

